text: Brná nad Labem (German: Birnai) is a part of city Ústí nad Labem, Czech republic. It is a small part of landscape park České středohoří on the right side of river Labe, and is close to Ústí nad Labem. Its area is about 4,23 km².Ministry of Interior of the Czech Republic.
